'''Wizard Entertainment''', previously '''Gareb Shamus Enterprises, Inc''', was the publisher of ''[[WIZARD Magazine]]'', ''[[InQuest Gamer]]'', ''[[ToyFare: The Toy Magazine]]'' and the distributor of both [[X-Wing_Rogue_Squadron_½|''X-Wing Rogue Squadron'' ½]] and [[Episode I: The Phantom Menace ½|''Episode I: The Phantom Menace'' ½]].
